<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">كثير:</span> أثبتها في الحالتين،<span class="c5"> والباقون:</span> حذفوها وقفًا ووصلًا، اتباعًا للرسم العثماني على لغة هذيل يجتزون بالكسرة عن الياء <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{عَلَى آَثَارِهِمَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٦٤]</span> تام.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>{قَصَصًا <span class="c2">(٦٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[٦٤]</span> جائز،<span class="c5"> أي:</span> يقُصَّان الأثر قصًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>{مِنْ لَدُنَّا عِلْمًا <span class="c2">(٦٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[٦٥]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«رشدًا»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>{مَعِيَ صَبْرًا <span class="c2">(٦٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[٦٧]</span> جائز،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«خبرًا»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{صَابِرًا}</span> <span class="c4">[٦٩]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لعطف ما بعده على ما قبله.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>{أَمْرًا <span class="c2">(٦٩)</span>} <span class="c4">[٦٩]</span> كاف.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>{مِنْهُ ذِكْرًا <span class="c2">(٧٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[٧٠]</span> جائز،<span class="c5"> ورسموا:</span> <span class="c3">{فإن اتَّبَعْتَنِي فَلَا تَسْأَلْنِي}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٠]</span> بياء.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c3">{فَانْطَلَقَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٧١]</span> أحسن مما قبله؛ لأنَّ <span class="c2">«حتى»</span> بعد <span class="c2">«إذا»</span> ابتدائية.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c3">{خَرَقَهَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٧١]</span> حسن.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c3">{لِتُغْرِقَ أَهْلَهَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٧١]</span> جائز.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>{إِمْرًا <span class="c2">(٧١)</span>} <span class="c4">[٧١]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«صبرًا»</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c3">{بِمَا نَسِيتُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٣]</span> جائز.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>{عُسْرًا <span class="c2">(٧٣)</span>} <span class="c4">[٧٣]</span> حسن.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c3">{فَانْطَلَقَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٤]</span> أحسن منه.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c3">{فَقَتَلَهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٤]</span> جائز،<span class="c5"> وقيل:</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ <span class="c2">«قال»</span> جواب <span class="c2">«إذا»</span>.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c3">{بِغَيْرِ نَفْسٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٤]</span> جائز، فصلًا بين الاستخبار والإخبار.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>{نُكْرًا <span class="c2">(٧٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[٧٤]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«معي صبرًا»</span>.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c3">{فَلَا تُصَاحِبْنِي}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٦]</span> جائز،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«عذرًا»</span>.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c3">{فَانْطَلَقَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٧]</span> أحسن، مما قبله.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c3">{فَأَقَامَهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٧]</span> جائز.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>{أَجْرًا <span class="c2">(٧٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[٧٧]</span> كاف.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c3">{بَيْنِي وَبَيْنِكَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٧٨]</span> حسن، على استئناف ما بعده.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>{صَبْرًا <span class="c2">(٧٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[٧٨]</span> تام.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
